Troubleshooting Tips
Tor Connection Issues:

Verify Tor service is running: sudo systemctl status tor
Check Tor logs: sudo journalctl -u tor -n 50
Test connection: curl --socks5-hostname 127.0.0.1:9050 https://check.torproject.org
Restart Tor if needed: sudo systemctl restart tor
Timeout Errors:

Increase timeout values in get_onion_content() function
Some .onion sites are slow; wait 30-60 seconds
Verify the .onion URL is accessible and active
Try accessing the site manually with Tor Browser first
JSON Parsing Errors:

Validate JSON syntax: python3 -m json.tool < file.json
Check for incomplete extractions due to timeouts
Ensure proper encoding handling for non-ASCII characters
Re-run extraction if metadata file is corrupted
Missing Dependencies:

Reinstall Python packages: pip3 install --upgrade requests beautifulsoup4 lxml
Check Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.6+)
Verify all imports work: python3 -c "import requests, bs4, json"
